    "m_ObjectId": "2cd0762b2e5240088f5f8ea4f0c9cc87",
    "m_Title": "2. Normals",
    "m_Content": "In the \"space\" menu of the node, select \"Object\".\nAt the out pin of this node, we have the three components of the vector which, at each point on the object, specifies its normal direction.",
